WEBVTT

00:03:57.085 --> 00:04:00.889
We humans are obsessed with speed.

00:04:01.236 --> 00:04:03.247
Busyness is a badge of honor,

00:04:03.271 --> 00:04:07.806
and convenience trumps quality
in our quest for quick.

00:04:08.553 --> 00:04:13.665
Our addiction to the express life
is choking us and the planet.

00:04:14.773 --> 00:04:20.093
We idolize animals like the cheetah,
the "Ferrari of the animal kingdom,"

00:04:20.117 --> 00:04:24.337
capable of doing naught to 60
in three seconds flat.

00:04:24.641 --> 00:04:25.941
Well, so what?

00:04:26.339 --> 00:04:30.007
(Laughter)